制令，拟于 4 月 4 日生效 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-144b82cd5f6afd67bd7f6ddc7e0f69c5_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/650881909"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1u6Rw6mb4Op9EAMaCTEwNjkxODM0OCCIuZ+wBjAAOPEJQBByCTY1MDg4MTkwOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1714403981.43932", "card_id": "Q_653888805", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一顿营养又制作简单的早餐是什么样子的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-97499ce8e7a02a48040ed79c165a39e3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653888805"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1u6Rw6mb4Op9EAMaCTEwNzU4NjMwNSCPiJ+xBjAAOB1AEXIJNjUzODg4ODA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1714403981.44838", "card_id": "Q_652499520", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "AI 将会促生哪些新的职业？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652499520"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1u6Rw6mb4Op9EAMaCTEwNzI3NzMxNCCcldmwBjAAOHhAEnIJNjUyNDk5NTIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "sty